      <body>
         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">The Free German Academy ¶ for Sciences, Arts and general Culture ¶ in Goethe's parental home ¶ to Baron Ferd von Mueller ¶ Director of the zoological-botanical garden...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="de">82.04.04</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="de">From the Freies Deutsches Hochstift</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="de">Freies Deutsches Hochstift Frankfurter Goethemuseum, Frankfurt am Main.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">Letter not found; MS is a file copy kept by the Academy. Annotated: 'Abschrift versandt Trappe' [Copy sent Trappe].</p>
               </note>
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times; ">Das Freie Deutsche Hochstift</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times; ">für Wissenschaften, Künste und allgemeine Bildung in </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times; ">Goethe's Vaterhause</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times; ">an </seg>Herrn Baron von Müller </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">Director des zool- botanischen Garten</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">Melbourne </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">Australien</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times; ">Frankfurt a. M., den</seg> 4 April <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times; ">18</seg>82</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times; ">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Unter bescheinigung des Empfanges Ihrer geehrten Zuschrift und Sendung vom</seg>10 Februar d Jr 2 B[uch] Pflanzenverzeichnisse des dortigen botanischen Gärten womit wir wieder einmal ein erfreulichen Lebenszeichen von Ihnen erhielten <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times; ">danken wir Ihnen verbindlichst und bitten um Erhaltung Ihres ferneren gütigen Wohlwollens für unsere Stiftung.</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times; ">Hochachtungsvoll zeichen</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times; ">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>für die Verwaltung</seg>:</p>
            <table n="Table1">
               <row>
                  <cell style="padding-left: 0.0556in; padding-right: 0.0556in; padding-top: 0in; padding-bottom: 0in; border: none; ">
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center; "
                        xml:lang="en">D B</p>
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times; ">d. Z. Obmann</seg>
                     </p>
                  </cell>
                  <cell style="padding-left: 0.0556in; padding-right: 0.0556in; padding-top: 0in; padding-bottom: 0in; border: none; ">
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 107%; text-align: center; "
                        xml:lang="en">L H</p>
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times; ">d. Z. Verwaltungsschreiber</seg>
                     </p>
                  </cell>
               </row>
            </table>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times; ">Trappe</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times; ">Schriftführer.</seg>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; text-align: center; "
               xml:lang="en">The Free German Academy</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; text-align: center; "
               xml:lang="en">for Sciences, Arts and general Culture</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; text-align: center; "
               xml:lang="en">in Goethe's parental home</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">to Baron Ferd von Mueller</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Director of the zoological-botanical garden</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Melbourne</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Australia</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Frankfurt on Main, 4 April 1882</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Under certification of receipt of your esteemed consignment of 10 February this year 2 [books] plant index of the local botanical gardens, by which we again receive a welcome sign of life from you we thank you kindly and request support of your further kindly goodwill for our academy.<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">It is possible that this letter was sent to the wrong person. No known work by M fits the description of the gift being acknowledged, while William Guilfoyle's catalogue of the plants growing in the Melbourne Botanic Garden — which, given M's continuing hostility towards Guilfoyle and his adminstration of the Garden, he is most unlikely to have sent anyway — was not published until 1883. Moreover, the comment about 'a welcome sign of life' seems inappropriate in relation to M, who had maintained regular contact with the Academy.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Respectfully signed</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>for the administration</p>
            <table n="Table2">
               <row>
                  <cell style="padding-left: 0.0556in; padding-right: 0.0556in; padding-top: 0in; padding-bottom: 0in; border: none; ">
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; text-align: center; "
                        xml:lang="en">D B<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                           <p rend="Footnote"
                              style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                              xml:lang="en">Carl Nicolas Berg. For this and the Clerk's name, see <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Berichte des Freien Deutsche Hochstiftes in Frankfurt am Main Jahrgang 1882-3</seg> (1884), p. 88.</p>
                        </note>
                     </p>
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; text-align: center; "
                        xml:lang="en">President at the time</p>
                  </cell>
                  <cell style="padding-left: 0.0556in; padding-right: 0.0556in; padding-top: 0in; padding-bottom: 0in; border: none; ">
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; text-align: center; "
                        xml:lang="en">L H<note xml:id="ftn4" type="footnote" n="4">
                           <p rend="Footnote"
                              style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                              xml:lang="en">Ludwig Holthof.</p>
                        </note>
                     </p>
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; text-align: center; "
                        xml:lang="en">Administrative clerk at the time</p>
                  </cell>
               </row>
            </table>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; text-align: center; "
               xml:lang="en">Trappe</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; text-align: center; "
               xml:lang="en">Secretary</p>
         </div>
      </body>
   </text>
